  Trust Badges Section
  
  A flexible trust badges section that displays multiple trust indicators
  (shipping, guarantees, support, quality, etc.) in a responsive grid.
  
  Features:
  - Supports multiple badges via blocks
  - Built-in icon library (Lucide Icons)
  - 15+ professional icons perfect for lifestyle brands
  - Fully customizable colors, spacing, and layout
  - Responsive grid (1-4 columns)
  - No external dependencies
